  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bb1\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b8e\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba3\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Don't forget the powers that people power has beyond the Constitution - warns Kumar Gunaratnam",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Even though there is a constitution, beyond that, the power lies with the power of the people. Kumar Gunaratnam, the General Secretary of the Front Socialist Party, has warned the political parties representing the Parliament that the political parties should not forget this.",
        "A few announcements have been made as the negotiations between the parties representing the Parliament on the appointment of a new Interim President and the selection of the Prime Minister are intensifying.",
        "Currently, the Rajapaksa regime, which was carried out contrary to democracy, has been overthrown by the people's spontaneous struggle.",
        "This is not just a struggle to oust the Rajapakses. Currently, Ranil Wickremesinghe, the representative of the Rajapaksas, is sitting on the throne. He is trying to usurp power.",
        "It is in such a situation that the protestors of Khalimaaktal have revealed their next plan of action. It has also been announced as a declaration.",
        "Therefore, the representatives of the political parties should take note of those matters. It is inappropriate for them to simply be at odds with each other for positions.",
        "Now there is an opportunity to change the political culture and system. It is not proper to ignore that opportunity.",
        "People power is built beyond the constitutional laws even though it is mentioned as acting according to the constitution. That power has authority.",
        "Therefore it is the duty of those in power to fulfill the demands and expectations of that power.",
        "National People's Assemblies should be created based on the people's power that is currently built.",
        "They should be inclusive of all the people of the country. He said that through that a new constitution should be created and solutions should be reached."
      ],
